    Signifies where the data came from, usually from a BLE read or notification.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      INDICATION
      Originates from BleDevice.enableNotify(BleNotify).
      MULTIPLE_MANUAL_ADDITIONS
      Originates from manual addition of data through BleDevice.addHistoricalData(UUID, java.util.Iterator) or various overloads that add multiple pieces of data all at once.
      NOTIFICATION
      Originates from BleDevice.enableNotify(BleNotify).
      NULL
      Satisfies soft contract of UsesCustomNull
      POLL
      Originates from BleDevice.startPoll(java.util.UUID, com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.utils.Interval, ReadWriteListener).
      PSUEDO_NOTIFICATION
      Originates from BleDevice.enableNotify(java.util.UUID, Interval, com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.ReadWriteListener), where a force-read timeout is invoked, or from BleDevice.startChangeTrackingPoll(java.util.UUID, com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.utils.Interval, ReadWriteListener).
      READ
      Originates from BleDevice.read(java.util.UUID, ReadWriteListener).
      SINGLE_MANUAL_ADDITION
      Originates from manual addition of data through BleDevice.addHistoricalData(UUID, byte[], EpochTime) or various overloads that add one piece of historical data.
